<subSubSection id="506097A5AA5B36EE92B8C711D4318D1A" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="8711C12529208AC23D0661573151A8FF" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="DA7FDB0434CB324F57CA2EC5C1F445EE" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">
<taxonomicName id="7B96A4EA81676F5E26C6FE8BF2DF01B9" baseAuthorityName="Bey-Bienko" baseAuthorityYear="1969" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Episymploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Episymploce kunmingi" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kunmingi">
<emphasis id="6224F4808CC2D84BED3C1AC423E00A6C" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Episymploce kunmingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was published by Bey-Bienko in 
<taxonomicName id="F23C364901346104B16F60A0848F7E32" authorityName="Hebard" authorityYear="1916" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Symploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Symploce" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="754895A99899A162BAADE782AC9919CD" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Symploce</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and was transferred to 
<taxonomicName id="039D978A9C863B31117B74FD7269CE41" authorityName="Bey-Bienko" authorityYear="1950" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Episymploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Episymploce" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="F0D22F94BB4ED2E0732164DA53346D55" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Episymploce</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="C118BE5D8C71C7B1B2BD56B5E0A77B2A" author="Roth, LM" journalOrPublisher="Entomologica Scandinavica" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" pagination="1 - 221" refId="B41" refString="Roth, LM, 1985b. A taxonomic revision of the genus Blattella Caudell (Dictyoptera, Blattaria: Blattellidae). Entomologica Scandinavica 22: 1 - 221" title="A taxonomic revision of the genus Blattella Caudell (Dictyoptera, Blattaria: Blattellidae)." volume="22" year="1985 b">Roth (1985b)</bibRefCitation>
based on the asymmetric T10. After examination of 
<taxonomicName id="E33462F84B8D8F5F7DCAABF3F90057B7" baseAuthorityName="Bey-Bienko" baseAuthorityYear="1969" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Episymploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Episymploce kunmingi" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kunmingi">
<emphasis id="3F7157C2DA08C34CC4A0B78AA809FDB5" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Episymploce kunmingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Bey-Bienko, 1969) and comparison with the holotype of 
<taxonomicName id="815875980276B3A75F0ED03510AD650B" authorityName="Woo &amp; P. Feng" authorityYear="1992" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Symploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Symploce quadrispinis" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadrispinis">
<emphasis id="7688DCB43E1FF428DAC26155C0EA8D63" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Symploce quadrispinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Woo and Feng, 1992, we found that there was no difference in their external morphology and male genitalia. So we regard 
<taxonomicName id="0A840351F159959955A88731CE8989E9" authorityName="Woo &amp; P. Feng" authorityYear="1992" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Symploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Symploce quadrispinis" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="quadrispinis">
<emphasis id="A4302C82F12CA3A7B92F11A966533D1F" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Symploce quadrispinis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as a synonym of 
<taxonomicName id="175D38BFD225AF5D857A8F90E1A23DB0" baseAuthorityName="Bey-Bienko" baseAuthorityYear="1969" class="Insecta" family="Blaberoidea" genus="Episymploce" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Episymploce kunmingi" order="Blattodea" pageId="0" pageNumber="187" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="kunmingi">
<emphasis id="AFF53F4138C5278A6F743BAAB9B42446" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="187">Episymploce kunmingi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Bey-Bienko, 1969).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
